      "value": "<p><em>Light and quick; better for parrying than turtling. Weak as a wall — it is a parry tool first.</em></p><p><strong>Block reduction (no roll):</strong> when you spend your reaction to Block, incoming damage of each type is reduced by this much, then dealt. Some moves are <em>unblockable</em> (100% through). A shield never staggers an enemy — that is parry's job.</p><table><tr><td><strong>Damage type</strong></td><td><strong>Reduced by</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Physical</td><td>50%</td></tr><tr><td>Fire</td><td>25%</td></tr><tr><td>Lightning</td><td>20%</td></tr><tr><td>Cold</td><td>25%</td></tr><tr><td>Poison</td><td>10%</td></tr></table>",
